originalText.text: Nicole is incredible.  I have been working with her on and off over the course of 5 years.  I first went to her for Mayan abdominal massage to help regulate my cycle.  And then, when my partner and I decided to try for a baby, I went back for accupuncture and massage.  I am not surprised that soon after my first appointment with her, we got our BFP.  She is now helping me through my pregnancy and she is such a gift.   I cannot recommend her enough!

originalText.text: Nicole is truly the best!!! Sweet, warm, thoughtful and  very talented. After 3 months of acupuncture she helped to DOUBLE the amount of eggs that were able to be retrieved. Something that neither the doctors nor I ever thought was possible. Thanks Nicole for giving me the most valuable gift of life- the ability to have kids:)

originalText.text: Nicole has been absolutely incredible in addressing a wide variety of issues for me. Even more so, she makes sure to create a safe and calm space for me to relax after a long day at work - critical! She really listens to me and asks follow up questions so as to provide a customized approach. I am so lucky to have found Nicole through a friend. Her experience shines through and her knowledge knows no bounds. Thank you, Nicole!!
